	"characterCreator.confirmExport.prompt": "The game will export your Sprite Project metadata, sprites, and animation data into a game-usable format. Depending on your hardware specifications, exporting will take from mere seconds to a VERY LONG TIME. Closing background programs can aid in accelerating the export rate.\n\nAfter the completion, all exported file assets will be stored in the exports folder in the game's root folder. Please keep this application open at all times during the export to prevent data corruption.\n\nAre you sure you want to export the project?",
